Class Keyword

java.lang.Object
  com.qualitestgroup.multiplan.kdt.Keyword
Direct Known Subclasses:
Browser.Close, Browser.GetElement, Browser.GetPageTitle, Browser.Launch, Browser.NavigateTo, Common.Validate, FNX.Login, FNX.Logout
public abstract class Keyword
extends Object

Abstract class for keywords. Implementing classes must provide override the exec function. The init and cleanup methods can be overridden to provide more functionality.

Author:
lenovo
